The paper discusses the use of WAN accelerators to improve the performance and power consumption of cloud computing environments. This involves optimizing data transfer over a network, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also discusses load balancing and power saving, which are topics related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and system dynamics (cs.SY). The use of machine learning algorithms to optimize power consumption falls under the category of deep learning (cs.DL). Finally, the paper discusses the use of different TCP connections, which is a topic related to computer communication (cs.CC).
